core

Class BWCIterator

  • java.lang.Object
    • core.BWCIterator

  • public class BWCIterator
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is an external iterator to support the naviation of BigWordCollection. The collection can not be modified. All the navigations are read-only. This is an external iterator and hence multiple iterators can be generated.
    Author:
    srj
